### Message API Tests
### Tests for MessageController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get session messages
### Returns all messages in a session
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/messages/{{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Send prompt to session
### Sends a user prompt/message to the AI session
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/messages/{{sessionId}}/prompt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parts": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Hello, can you help me with my Java code?"
    }
  ],
  "agent": "opencode",
  "model": "glm-4.7"
}

###

### Send prompt with file reference
### Sends a prompt that includes file context
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/messages/{{sessionId}}/prompt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parts": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Please review this file:"
    },
    {
      "type": "file",
      "path": "src/main/java/opencode/Main.java"
    }
  ],
  "agent": "opencode"
}

###

### Abort session message
### Aborts the current ongoing message generation
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/messages/{{sessionId}}/abort
Content-Type: application/json

###
